                              <locus target="#9r"/> Note that the age of <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገብረ፡ ክረስቶስ፡</foreign> was 73 years on the feast day of Abbo in the month of Ṭəqəmt (5 Ṭəqəmt)</desc>
