                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <desc type="Asmat">
                              <locus target="#9v"/> Asmat prayer against hemorrhage (and for bladder control), with incipit
                        <foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡...ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ደም፡ ወማይ፡ ሰይፍ፡ ወአዶናይ፡...ሎፍሐም፡ መሕፍሎን፡ ደመ፡ ዓቤል፡ ደመ፡ ትክቶ፡ ደመ፡ ንስር፡ ሄት፡ ትኖሯለሽ፡...</foreign>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a7">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#117v"/> Prayer of <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ካህን፡</foreign> that God may not separate him (by death) from the community</desc>
                        </item>
